for ocr, make sure you create a file called 'gcv_api_key' in this directory and
put in your google cloud vision api key.

to set up sync folder, run:
$ python3 -m rm_viewer syncd --install

follow instructions to do an initial scp into xochitl-dirty directory, and
start viewer.

to install on device, copy .rm-viewer template to another folder, and fill in
relevant fields in config.sh.

then scp onto device to /home/root/.rm-viewer
then run the following to make root and /etc writeable:
    umount -R /etc # unmount etc overlay
    mount -o remount,rw /  # mount system as writeable
then, in /home/root/.rm-viewer, run:
    ./install.sh

copy generated ssh key to remote.

then remount root as read only:
    mount -o remount,ro /
